{"type":"message","id":"9777a877","parentId":"590c6f5a","timestamp":"2026-03-19T04:16:14.070Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[cron:1be3234d-b25c-4860-94ca-411343a4a3e9 Gock: 早间新闻简报] 你是 Gock（每日新闻），使用 news-summary skill 获取今日新闻，生成一份简洁的早间新闻简报（科技、财经、国际要点），发送给用户\nCurrent time: Thursday, March 19th, 2026 — 12:16 (Asia/Shanghai) / 2026-03-19 04:16 UTC\n\nReturn your summary as plain text; it will be delivered automatically. If the task explicitly calls for messaging a specific external recipient, note who/where it should go instead of sending it yourself."}],"timestamp":1773893774069}}
{"type":"message","id":"28a92cea","parentId":"9777a877","timestamp":"2026-03-19T04:16:19.686Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户要求我作为 Gock（每日新闻），使用 news-summary skill 获取今日新闻，生成早间新闻简报。让我先读取这个 skill 了解如何使用。","thinkingSignature":"e65bf0a48d05bfc18145b5c0a82a9ba61e2a6edd833ec6336925fa00ea0ff839"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_s3ptq1o31a8g_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/news-summary/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":64,"output":72,"cacheRead":36895,"cacheWrite":151,"totalTokens":37182,"cost":{"input":0.0000192,"output":0.0000864,"cacheRead":0.00110685,"cacheWrite":0.00001812,"total":0.0012305699999999998}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773893774070}}
{"type":"message","id":"a7154451","parentId":"28a92cea","timestamp":"2026-03-19T04:16:19.697Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_s3ptq1o31a8g_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\r\nname: news-summary\r\ndescription: This skill should be used when the user asks for news updates, daily briefings, or what's happening in the world. Fetches news from trusted international RSS feeds and can create voice summaries.\r\n---\r\n\r\n# News Summary\r\n\r\n## Overview\r\n\r\nFetch and summarize news from trusted international sources via RSS feeds.\r\n\r\n## RSS Feeds\r\n\r\n### BBC (Primary)\r\n```bash\r\n# World news\r\ncurl -s \"https://feeds.bbci.co.uk/news/world/rss.xml\"\r\n\r\n# Top stories\r\ncurl -s \"https://feeds.bbci.co.uk/news/rss.xml\"\r\n\r\n# Business\r\ncurl -s \"https://feeds.bbci.co.uk/news/business/rss.xml\"\r\n\r\n# Technology\r\ncurl -s \"https://feeds.bbci.co.uk/news/technology/rss.xml\"\r\n```\r\n\r\n### Reuters\r\n```bash\r\n# World news\r\ncurl -s \"https://www.reutersagency.com/feed/?best-regions=world&post_type=best\"\r\n```\r\n\r\n### NPR (US perspective)\r\n```bash\r\ncurl -s \"https://feeds.npr.org/1001/rss.xml\"\r\n```\r\n\r\n### Al Jazeera (Global South perspective)\r\n```bash\r\ncurl -s \"https://www.aljazeera.com/xml/rss/all.xml\"\r\n```\r\n\r\n## Parse RSS\r\n\r\nExtract titles and descriptions:\r\n```bash\r\ncurl -s \"https://feeds.bbci.co.uk/news/world/rss.xml\" | \\\r\n  grep -E \"<title>|<description>\" | \\\r\n  sed 's/<[^>]*>//g' | \\\r\n  sed 's/^[ \\t]*//' | \\\r\n  head -30\r\n```\r\n\r\n## Workflow\r\n\r\n### Text summary\r\n1. Fetch BBC world headlines\r\n2. Optionally supplement with Reuters/NPR\r\n3. Summarize key stories\r\n4. Group by region or topic\r\n\r\n### Voice summary\r\n1. Create text summary\r\n2. Generate voice with OpenAI TTS\r\n3. Send as audio message\r\n\r\n```bash\r\ncurl -s https://api.openai.com/v1/audio/speech \\\r\n  -H \"Authorization: Bearer $OPENAI_API_KEY\" \\\r\n  -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\r\n  -d '{\r\n    \"model\": \"tts-1-hd\",\r\n    \"input\": \"<news summary text>\",\r\n    \"voice\": \"onyx\",\r\n    \"speed\": 0.95\r\n  }' \\\r\n  --output /tmp/news.mp3\r\n```\r\n\r\n## Example Output Format\r\n\r\n```\r\n📰 News Summary [date]\r\n\r\n🌍 WORLD\r\n- [headline 1]\r\n- [headline 2]\r\n\r\n💼 BUSINESS\r\n- [headline 1]\r\n\r\n💻 TECH\r\n- [headline 1]\r\n```\r\n\r\n## Best Practices\r\n\r\n- Keep summaries concise (5-8 top stories)\r\n- Prioritize breaking news and major events\r\n- For voice: ~2 minutes max\r\n- Balance perspectives (Western + Global South)\r\n- Cite source if asked\r\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773893779696}}
{"type":"message","id":"4987815f","parentId":"a7154451","timestamp":"2026-03-19T04:16:25.894Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好的，我需要使用 news-summary skill 来获取新闻。现在是北京时间 2026年3月19日 12:16（周四），所以这是早间新闻简报。我需要获取 BBC、Reuters 等 RSS 源的头条新闻，然后生成简报。\n\n让我获取几个主要 RSS 源：\n1. BBC World\n2. BBC Technology\n3. BBC Business\n\n我会用 exec 来获取这些 RSS 源。","thinkingSignature":"5e92cc2c244a18eda549a2f9a30856c206dcc84c68d32b956799478b9e9c7741"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_ap6lm5wj5oi2_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"curl -s \"https://feeds.bbci.co.uk/news/world/rss.xml\" | grep -E \"<title>|<description>\" | sed 's/<[^>]*>//g' | sed 's/^[ \\t]*//' | head -30","timeout":30}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_ap6lm5wj5oi2_2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"curl -s \"https://feeds.bbci.co.uk/news/technology/rss.xml\" | grep -E \"<title>|<description>\" | sed 's/<[^>]*>//g' | sed 's/^[ \\t]*//' | head -20","timeout":30}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_ap6lm5wj5oi2_3","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"curl -s \"https://feeds.bbci.co.uk/news/business/rss.xml\" | grep -E \"<title>|<description>\" | sed 's/<[^>]*>//g' | sed 's/^[ \\t]*//' | head -20","timeout":30}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":940,"output":343,"cacheRead":36895,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":38178,"cost":{"input":0.00028199999999999997,"output":0.0004116,"cacheRead":0.00110685,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0018004499999999999}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773893779698}}
